rows.label: tlk45320391_01_msg0001
rows.name:
His Majesty gave the order to halt
all Divine Beast weapon excavation, but
Senator Roderich went ahead anyway.

rows.label: tlk45320391_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Since it's all unofficial, we never got
sent any powerful Driver soldiers
to back us up or anything.

rows.label: tlk45320391_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So of course we were never going to be
able to face up to the likes of Iira!

rows.label: tlk45320391_01_msg0004
rows.name:
He just doesn't know how to
manage a crisis at all.
Don't tell anyone I said that, mind.
